{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":4240,"text":"\"You have cancer.\""},{"time":8680,"text":"Sadly, about 40 percent of us will hear\nthose three words within our lifetime,"},{"time":13840,"text":"and half will not survive."},{"time":16960,"text":"This means that two out of five\nof your closest friends and relatives"},{"time":20840,"text":"will be diagnosed\nwith some form of cancer,"},{"time":23320,"text":"and one will die."},{"time":27280,"text":"Beyond the physical hardships,"},{"time":28760,"text":"roughly one-third\nof cancer survivors here in the US"},{"time":31960,"text":"will go into debt from treatment."},{"time":33720,"text":"And they're at least two and a half times\nmore likely to declare bankruptcy"},{"time":37480,"text":"than those without cancer."},{"time":39680,"text":"This disease is pervasive."},{"time":42080,"text":"It's emotionally draining"},{"time":43680,"text":"and, for many,"},{"time":44920,"text":"financially destructive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47880,"text":"But a cancer diagnosis\ndoesn't have to be a death sentence."},{"time":51920,"text":"Finding cancer early,"},{"time":53800,"text":"closer its genesis,"},{"time":55040,"text":"is one of the critical factors\nto improving treatment options,"},{"time":58680,"text":"reducing its emotional impact"},{"time":60680,"text":"and minimizing financial burdens."},{"time":63560,"text":"Most importantly,"},{"time":64800,"text":"finding cancer early --"},{"time":66080,"text":"which is one of the primary\naims of my research --"},{"time":69000,"text":"greatly enhances your odds of survival."},{"time":72120,"text":"If we just look at the case\nof breast cancer for example,"},{"time":74880,"text":"we find that those who are diagnosed\nand treated at stage one"},{"time":78400,"text":"have a five-year survival rate\nof nearly 100 percent --"},{"time":82760,"text":"odds that decrease to just 22 percent\nif treated at stage four."},{"time":88040,"text":"And similar trends are found\nfor colorectal and ovarian cancer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94000,"text":"Now, we're all aware\nthat an early diagnosis that is accurate"},{"time":99480,"text":"is critical for survival."},{"time":103600,"text":"The problem is that many\ncancer diagnostic tools are invasive,"},{"time":107440,"text":"costly,"},{"time":108680,"text":"often inaccurate"},{"time":109920,"text":"and they can take an agonizing\namount of time to get the results back."},{"time":114520,"text":"Still worse, when it comes\nto some forms of cancer,"},{"time":116960,"text":"such as ovarian,\nliver or pancreatic cancer,"},{"time":121280,"text":"good screening methods simply don't exist,"},{"time":124880,"text":"meaning that often people wait\nuntil physical symptoms surface,"},{"time":128960,"text":"which are themselves already\nindicators of late-stage progression."},{"time":133920,"text":"Like a tornado strike in an area\nwithout an early warning system,"},{"time":137520,"text":"there is no alarm to warn,"},{"time":139440,"text":"for the danger is already at your doorstep"},{"time":142320,"text":"when your odds of survival\nare greatly reduced."},{"time":147400,"text":"Having the convenience and accessibility\nof regular screening options"},{"time":151680,"text":"that are affordable, noninvasive\nand could provide results much sooner,"},{"time":157040,"text":"would provide us with a formidable\nweapon in the fight against cancer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162760,"text":"An early warning would allow us\nto get out ahead of the disease"},{"time":165840,"text":"instead of merely\nfollowing in its relentless wake."},{"time":168600,"text":"And this is exactly what I've been doing."},{"time":170600,"text":"For the past three years,\nI've been developing technologies"},{"time":173760,"text":"that could ultimately aid clinicians"},{"time":175520,"text":"with rapid, early-stage\ncancer diagnostics."},{"time":178920,"text":"And I've been fueled\nby a deep scientific curiosity,"},{"time":182800,"text":"and a passion to change these statistics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186880,"text":"Last year however,"},{"time":188960,"text":"this fight became much more personal"},{"time":192040,"text":"when my wife was diagnosed\nwith breast cancer."},{"time":195560,"text":"It was an experience that added a strong\nand unexpected emotional dimension"},{"time":200000,"text":"to these efforts."},{"time":203240,"text":"I know firsthand how life-altering\ntreatment can be,"},{"time":207520,"text":"and I'm keenly aware\nof the emotional havoc"},{"time":210200,"text":"that cancer can wreak on a family,"},{"time":212680,"text":"which in our case\nincluded our two young daughters."},{"time":216400,"text":"Because we found it early\nduring a routine mammogram,"},{"time":219560,"text":"we were able to focus\nprimarily on treatment options"},{"time":223280,"text":"for the localized tumor,"},{"time":224840,"text":"reaffirming to me\nhow important an early diagnosis is."},{"time":230960,"text":"Unlike other forms of cancer,"},{"time":233400,"text":"mammograms do offer an early-stage\nscreening option for breast cancer."},{"time":237080,"text":"Still, not everyone has this done,"},{"time":239320,"text":"or they may develop breast cancer"},{"time":240930,"text":"before the middle age recommendation\nfor having a mammogram."},{"time":245560,"text":"So, there's still\na lot of room for improvement,"},{"time":247840,"text":"even for cancers\nthat do have screening options,"},{"time":250120,"text":"and, of course, considerable benefits\nfor those that don't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":253680,"text":"A key challenge then\nfor cancer researchers"},{"time":256440,"text":"is to develop methods"},{"time":257760,"text":"that make regular screening\nfor many types of cancers"},{"time":261320,"text":"much more accessible."},{"time":263920,"text":"Imagine a scenario\nwhere during your regular checkup,"},{"time":267000,"text":"your doctor can take\na simple, noninvasive urine sample,"},{"time":270800,"text":"or other liquid biopsy,"},{"time":272720,"text":"and present you with the results\nbefore you even leave the doctor's office."},{"time":276800,"text":"Such a technology could\ndramatically reduce the number of people"},{"time":280360,"text":"who slip through the net\nof an early-stage cancer diagnosis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":284840,"text":"My research team\nof engineers and biochemists"},{"time":287680,"text":"is working on exactly this challenge."},{"time":290320,"text":"We're working on ways to frequently\nactivate an early-stage cancer alarm"},{"time":295480,"text":"by enabling regular screenings\nthat would start when a person is healthy"},{"time":299840,"text":"so that action could be taken\nto stop cancer the moment it emerges,"},{"time":304160,"text":"and before it can progress\nbeyond its infancy."},{"time":308640,"text":"The silver bullet in this case\nare tiny vesicles,"},{"time":311680,"text":"little escape pods regularly shed\nby cells called exosomes."},{"time":316680,"text":"Exosomes are important biomarkers"},{"time":319440,"text":"that provide an early-warning system\nfor the development of cancer."},{"time":323720,"text":"And because they're abundantly present\nin just about every bodily fluid,"},{"time":327160,"text":"including blood, urine and saliva,"},{"time":329680,"text":"they're extremely attractive\nfor noninvasive liquid biopsies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335040,"text":"There's just one problem."},{"time":336640,"text":"An automated system for rapidly sorting\nthese important biomarkers"},{"time":340960,"text":"is not currently available."},{"time":343680,"text":"We've created a technology\nthat we call nano-DLD"},{"time":347000,"text":"that is capable of precisely this:"},{"time":349920,"text":"automated exosome isolation"},{"time":352640,"text":"to aid rapid cancer diagnostics."},{"time":356040,"text":"Exosomes are the newest\nearly-warning weapon, if you will,"},{"time":359600,"text":"to emerge on the liquid biopsy front."},{"time":361680,"text":"And they're really, really small."},{"time":364000,"text":"They measure just 30 to 150\nnanometers in diameter."},{"time":368280,"text":"This is so tiny"},{"time":369600,"text":"that you could fit about a million\nof them into a single red blood cell."},{"time":373800,"text":"That's roughly the difference\nbetween a golf ball"},{"time":376160,"text":"and a fine grain piece of sand."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378920,"text":"Once thought to be little bins\nfor unwanted cellular waste,"},{"time":382640,"text":"it has been found\nthat cells actually communicate"},{"time":385640,"text":"by producing and absorbing these exosomes"},{"time":388800,"text":"which contain surface receptors,"},{"time":391200,"text":"proteins and other genetic material\ncollected from their cell of origin."},{"time":396520,"text":"When absorbed by a neighboring cell,"},{"time":399200,"text":"exosomes release their contents\ninto the receiving cell,"},{"time":403040,"text":"and can set in motion\nfundamental changes in gene expression --"},{"time":406280,"text":"some good,"},{"time":407520,"text":"and this is where cancer comes in,"},{"time":409280,"text":"some bad."},{"time":410880,"text":"Because they are clothed\nin the material of the mother cell,"},{"time":414680,"text":"and contain a sample of its environment,"},{"time":416640,"text":"they provide a genetic snapshot\nof that cell's health and its origin."},{"time":423200,"text":"All of these qualities\nmake exosomes invaluable messengers"},{"time":426360,"text":"that potentially allow physicians"},{"time":428000,"text":"to eavesdrop on your health\nat the cellular level."}]},{"cues":[{"time":432080,"text":"To catch cancer early, however,"},{"time":433760,"text":"you have to frequently\nintercept these messages"},{"time":436720,"text":"to determine when cancer-causing\ntroublemakers within your body"},{"time":440240,"text":"decide to start staging a coup,"},{"time":442080,"text":"which is why regular\nscreening is so critical"},{"time":445120,"text":"and why we're developing\ntechnologies to make this possible."},{"time":449120,"text":"While the first exosome-based diagnostics\nemerged on the market just this year,"},{"time":454800,"text":"they are not yet part\nof mainstream healthcare options."},{"time":459320,"text":"In addition to their recent emergence,"},{"time":461200,"text":"another factor that's limiting\ntheir widespread adoption"},{"time":464680,"text":"is that currently, no automated\nexosome isolation system exists"},{"time":468640,"text":"to make regular screening\neconomically accessible."},{"time":472800,"text":"The current gold standard\nfor exosome isolation"},{"time":475560,"text":"includes ultracentrifugation,"},{"time":477520,"text":"a process requiring\nexpensive laboratory equipment,"},{"time":480800,"text":"a trained lab tech"},{"time":482080,"text":"and about 30 hours of time\nto process a sample."},{"time":486600,"text":"We've come up with a different approach\nfor achieving automated exosome isolation"},{"time":491280,"text":"from a sample such as urine."},{"time":493560,"text":"We use a chip-based, continuous flow\nseparation technique"},{"time":497840,"text":"called deterministic lateral displacement."},{"time":500840,"text":"And we have done with it"},{"time":502240,"text":"what the semiconductor industry has done\nso successfully for the past 50 years."},{"time":506720,"text":"We shrunk the dimensions\nof this technology"},{"time":508800,"text":"from the micron scale\nto the true nanoscale."}]},{"cues":[{"time":512720,"text":"So how does it work?"},{"time":514200,"text":"In a nutshell,"},{"time":515480,"text":"a set of tiny pillars\nseparated by nanoscopic gaps"},{"time":519480,"text":"are arranged in such a way"},{"time":520760,"text":"that the system divides\nthe fluid into streamlines,"},{"time":523840,"text":"with the larger cancer-related\nnanoparticles being separated"},{"time":527240,"text":"through a process of redirection\nfrom the smaller, healthier ones,"},{"time":531160,"text":"which can in contrast"},{"time":532720,"text":"move around the pillars\nin a zigzag-type motion"},{"time":535280,"text":"in the direction of fluid flow."},{"time":538080,"text":"The net result is a complete separation\nof these two particle populations."},{"time":543440,"text":"You can visualize this separation process"},{"time":547160,"text":"similar to traffic on a highway\nthat separates into two roads,"},{"time":551040,"text":"with one road going into\na low-clearance tunnel under a mountain,"},{"time":554520,"text":"and the other road going around it."},{"time":556600,"text":"Here, smaller cars\ncan go through the tunnel"},{"time":559400,"text":"while larger trucks,\ncarrying potentially hazardous material,"},{"time":562720,"text":"are forced to take the detour route."},{"time":565600,"text":"Traffic is effectively separated\nby size and contents"},{"time":569720,"text":"without impeding its flow."},{"time":571760,"text":"And this is exactly how our system works\non a much, much smaller scale."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577600,"text":"The idea here is that\nthe separation process for screening"},{"time":581480,"text":"could be as simple as processing\na sample of urine, blood or saliva,"},{"time":585560,"text":"which is a near-term possibility\nwithin the next few years."},{"time":588880,"text":"Ultimately, it could be used\nto isolate and detect target exosomes"},{"time":594200,"text":"associated with\na particular type of cancer,"},{"time":597440,"text":"sensing and reporting\ntheir presence within minutes."},{"time":600600,"text":"This would make rapid diagnostics\nvirtually painless."},{"time":604720,"text":"Broadly speaking,"},{"time":606000,"text":"the ability to separate\nand enrich biomarkers"},{"time":608680,"text":"with nanoscale precision\nin an automated way,"},{"time":612320,"text":"opens the door to better understanding\ndiseases such as cancer,"},{"time":615800,"text":"with applications ranging\nfrom sample preparation to diagnostics,"},{"time":619800,"text":"and from drug resistance\nmonitoring to therapeutics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":623440,"text":"Even before my wife's bout with cancer,"},{"time":625480,"text":"it was a dream of mine to facilitate\nthe automation of this process --"},{"time":629840,"text":"to make regular screening more accessible,"},{"time":632800,"text":"similar to the way Henry Ford\nmade the automobile accessible"},{"time":635720,"text":"to the general population"},{"time":637320,"text":"through development of the assembly line."},{"time":639600,"text":"Automation is the key to accessibility."},{"time":644280,"text":"And in the spirit of the Hoover dream,"},{"time":646160,"text":"\"a chicken in every pot\nand a car in every garage,\""},{"time":649080,"text":"we're developing a technology"},{"time":650520,"text":"that could ultimately place\nan early-warning cancer detection system"},{"time":654360,"text":"in every home."},{"time":656000,"text":"This would allow\nevery man, woman and child"},{"time":658080,"text":"the opportunity to be regularly tested\nwhile they're still healthy,"},{"time":662240,"text":"catching cancer when it first emerges."}]},{"cues":[{"time":665400,"text":"It is my hope and dream"},{"time":666920,"text":"to help people around the world\navoid the high costs --"},{"time":670640,"text":"physical, financial and emotional --"},{"time":673200,"text":"faced by today's cancer patients,"},{"time":675600,"text":"hardships that I'm well acquainted with."},{"time":679400,"text":"I'm also happy to report that because\nwe caught my wife's cancer early,"},{"time":683800,"text":"her treatment was successful,"},{"time":685480,"text":"and she is now, thankfully, cancer-free."}]},{"cues":[{"time":687760,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":696160,"text":"It is an outcome that I would like to see\nfor everyone with a cancer diagnosis."},{"time":701280,"text":"With the work that my team\nhas already done"},{"time":703360,"text":"on separation of nanoscale biomarkers"},{"time":706120,"text":"for rapid, early-stage cancer diagnostics,"},{"time":709080,"text":"I am optimistic\nthat within the next decade,"},{"time":711640,"text":"this type of technology will be available,"},{"time":714240,"text":"helping protect our friends,\nour family and future generations."},{"time":718680,"text":"Even if we are so unlucky\nas to be diagnosed with cancer,"},{"time":722600,"text":"that early-stage alarm\nwill provide a strong beacon of hope."}]},{"cues":[{"time":726280,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":727520,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}